<i>Posted by Sariss on 12-22-2000 01:35 AM:</i>

<p><b> </b></p>

<p><br>
Greetings,<br>
<br>
LegionOfCabilis is the Warriors (Troopers)<br>
CitizensOfCabilis (merchants?)<br>
ScaledMystics (shamans)<br>
<br>
Since you are dubious to the troopers, if you go to the Field of bone... and to the Cabilis entrance... the Trooper to the RIGHT side of the zone in has a quest... give him 4 bone chips... you get faction hits with almost every faction group ( I think it is missing necros... ).  Be careful though, there are shadow knights around (Crusaders)... as an Iksar, my faction started higher with troopers than crusaders.<br><FONT face="arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><br>
