<i>Posted by Fulaq on 12-22-2000 04:41 PM:</i>

<p><b> Damn innoruk and double bone chips</b></p>

<p>I was just about to do a huge Cabilis Faction post but Ysgwyrthyr got there before me <img src="images/smilies/biggrin.gif" border="0" alt=""><br>
<br>
Couple of things he didn't mention.....<br>
<br>
It took him 4000 chips it will take you 8000 to be able to trade. (Same as me coz I worship inny).<br>
<br>
You don't have to do just bopne chips any more since the faction patch, you can do any of the Legion quests (but bone chips is still probably best).<br>
<br>
The alchemy vendors are in West Cabilis.<br>
<br>
The necro Grype is level 30 so if you are a sufficient level, then he won't aggro.<br>
<br>
Another good place to collect bone chips is Paineel as the newbie ground has insta spawn decaying skellys if you are far enough away from the spawn point. I got my 8000 chips here and it took me about 40 hours online time so maybe it is better going here than Kurns (Kurns would be more fun though).<br>
<br>
That's all I can think of for now....<br>
<br>
As far as I know me and Ysg are the only two trolls on CT that can get into Cabilis <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt=""><br>
