<i>Posted by Fulaq on 01-17-2001 11:00 AM:</i>

<p><b> Careful</b></p>

<p>Be careful camping near guards and NPC's there is a bug which happens very occasionally, when you log in the game loads your gained faction as you enter the world, if this doesn't sync properly you will be KOS for about 0.5 seconds, if they aggro you in this time, you will stay aggroed.<br>
<br>
PS the necro in E cab is too low level to aggro you<FONT face="arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><br>
