6,000 bonechips till you can train<br>
<br>
7,600 bonechips till you can buy spells<br>
<br>
8,000 bonechips till you can get good prices<br>
<br>
(Above only applies to Barbie shammies)<br>
<br>
So yes a hell of a long way.<FONT face="arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><br>
