<i>Posted by Bini on 01-21-2001 05:40 PM:</i>

<p><b> By the way.....</b></p>

<p>I have found that the easiest way to collect bone chips is to grab all of your "monk junk" out of you bank.  Then go to FOB, and auction Item 1 for x number of bone chips, Item 2 for y number of bone chips....and so on.  Let everyone know that you will be back in 5 to 6 hours to trade.  Come back in 5 hours and collect your bone chips =).<br>
<br>
Same thing with necro stuff for Painel.<br>
<br>
Works like a charm, and more effective then just offering money.<br>
<br>
Bini Da'Meanie</p>
